data.description: No access will be permitted without an accepted contract. This up/down duplex already has separate entries to both units, two gas meters, and two electrical meters. Renovate the home and move in and rent out the other unit. Also has an oversized 2 car detached garage off the alley. Existing structure does not need to be scraped, but it will require a lot of work. Zoned R-2, so you could scrape and build a new side-by-side duplex if desired. Located in the heart of Edgewater and within walkable distance to the best eateries and breweries in Edgewater and only a handful of blocks from the highly desirable Sloan's Lake. Seller is selling in as-is condition and will not make any repairs. Please reach out for photos and videos.
